# starcitizen-scmdb environment configuration
#
# No API keys are required to run this skill.
# All data sources used (SCMDB, SC Wiki, UEX Corp) have public endpoints
# that work without authentication.
#
# ── Future / optional ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────
# UEX Corp token — enables user-specific features not yet implemented:
#   - Blueprint ownership tracking (owned vs. unowned)
#   - Personal trade history and analytics
#   - Price submission to the community database
#   - Watchlists and price alerts
#
# To enable these in a future release:
#   1. Create a free account at https://uexcorp.space
#   2. Go to https://uexcorp.space/api/apps and create an app
#   3. Copy your Bearer token below and rename this file to .env
#
# UEX_API_TOKEN=your_token_here
